Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:10.90,japanese,,0,0,0,,(シズネ)綱手様！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:14.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,防御結界 転生術\Nすべての術が解かれ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.89,0:00:17.89,japanese,,0,0,0,,大門付近は\N平静を 取り戻しつつあります。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.89,0:00:21.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,それから…\Nアスマさんからの 報告にあった➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.23,0:00:24.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,里を 一瞬のうちに\N焼き尽くすという 敵の術も➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.25,0:00:26.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,実行前に 阻止できたもようです！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:28.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,(綱手)そうか…。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.20,0:00:35.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,(綱手)なんだ!? あの 赤い光は！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:37.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,えっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.90,0:01:15.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)ぐぉぉぉ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.55,0:01:17.55,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.24,0:02:56.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,アスマ先生… これは いったい…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.74,0:02:58.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,わからん…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.38,japanese,,0,0,0,,いいぞ ソラ！ 怒れ！ 恨め！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:10.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,その怒りを… その恨みを\N力に変えろ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)木ノ葉の里の者どもに\N叩きつけてやれ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:16.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)ヤツらを 死に追いやるんだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.39,0:03:18.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,ふざけるな…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.39,0:03:21.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは… そんなことのために…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,生まれてきたんじゃ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,きたんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.24,0:03:30.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,すべては 火ノ国を\N真に 統一するためにこそある。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.74,0:03:35.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前の力が 今こそ必要なんだよ。\Nソラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:39.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,なに わけ わかんねえこと\N言ってんだ テメエ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:41.21,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前…。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,((カズマ : アスマ～!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:56.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,(カズマ～!!))
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:59.57,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんな… お前は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.07,0:04:06.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,アスマ先生…\N知ってるのか？ コイツのこと…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.73,0:04:08.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,…あぁ。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:12.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,(アスマ)かつての 守護忍十二士の…\N同志だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:17.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前…\Nお前 ソラに いったい 何をした!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.87,0:04:22.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,キサマの おこぼれに\Nあずかったまでさ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.24,0:04:24.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,…なんだって!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.56,japanese,,0,0,0,,フッ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:29.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)ソラは… キサマと同じ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.72,0:04:33.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,やめろ～!!\Nうわぁぁぁ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… ぐぅ～っ…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.91,0:04:58.39,japanese,,0,0,0,,くっ… うぅ～っ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.39,0:05:00.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.41,0:05:02.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,くっ… うわ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.41,0:05:05.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,あっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.42,0:05:07.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんなんだよ… この痛みは…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.74,0:05:14.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは… 本当に…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.09,0:05:18.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは… 九尾に…！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:22.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前…\Nいったい どうやって ソラに…!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:27.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,ヘッヘッヘッヘッ…\N九尾が 木ノ葉を襲ったのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.29,0:05:30.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレよりゃ お前のほうが\N詳しいわな。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:35.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)あのとき 九尾は\N四代目 火影の命と引き替えに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.41,0:05:38.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,１人の赤子に 封印された…。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:42.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉は ついに\N九尾を 手に入れやがった。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:46.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレたちも そのチャンスを\N逃す手はねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:49.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)九尾が 暴れ回ったとき\Nばらまかれた チャクラを➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.73,0:05:52.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレたちは 手に入れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.40,0:05:55.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,それを培養し ５年後➡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.22,0:05:57.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラに 植えつけたのさ。
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:06:00.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前… ソラは お前の…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.84,0:06:02.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)それが どうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:07.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,木ノ葉だって\N大きな力を 手に入れたんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:11.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)オレたちだって\N玉を守るために 力を手に入れた。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,(フリド)それの 何が悪い？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:16.07,japanese,,0,0,0,,ううっ…！ ぐわっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:22.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:24.08,japanese,,0,0,0,,わかってた…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.08,0:06:28.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうだよ… わかってたんだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.09,0:06:34.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,なのに… オレは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:42.75,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれは… あれは ソラの…\N泣き叫ぶ声だって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.75,0:06:47.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,なのに… なんで オレは\N気づいてやれなかったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:51.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,コイツの痛みに… 叫びに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレにしか\Nわかってやれなかったのに…。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐっ ぐぅぅぅ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.26,0:07:01.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,あんときだって そうだった。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.25,0:07:05.42,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラを見る 周りの目…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,冷たくて ぞっとして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:12.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,ここから出てけって\N言ってるみてえな…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:22.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,同じって…\Nわかってたじゃねえか。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.10,0:07:27.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが\Nずっと受けていた あの目と…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:44.73,japanese,,0,0,0,,さんざん オレを\N突き刺すように見てきた➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:48.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,大人たちの あの目…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.10,0:07:50.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの目と同じじゃねえか！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:54.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,それが どうした？ 今さら…。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.94,0:07:56.91,japanese,,0,0,0,,その目だよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.91,0:08:01.78,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレたちを バケモノとしか見てねえ\Nその目が オレたちを孤独にした！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.78,0:08:07.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,そのうえ… テメエらの\N勝手な都合で利用しようとして…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,ううっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.27,0:08:14.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,我愛羅のときもそうだ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.26,0:08:17.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうして お前たち大人はよ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.26,0:08:20.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレたちの気持を\N考えようともしねえ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:23.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,しかも ソラは… ソラは…。
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:29.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,このバケモノを入れる必要が\Nどこにあんだ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうして… どうして ソラに…！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.09,0:08:47.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,うるせえなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:55.61,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:07.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:12.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,近寄るな！ 誰も オレに近寄るな！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.93,0:09:20.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,冗談じゃねえぞ…\Nもう騙されねえ。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.26,0:09:24.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,父さんを殺しておいて…\N平気な顔で オレに近づき…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.28,0:09:31.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,何が特別な力だ！ 騙しやがって！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:34.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。\N近寄るなって言ったろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:36.87,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前だって…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.87,0:09:39.76,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前だって 所詮 木ノ葉の者だ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,信用できるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.74,0:09:44.05,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐっ… ぐぅぅ…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.27,0:09:52.24,japanese,,0,0,0,,なっ 何だってば…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:03.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁぁぁっ…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.10,0:10:05.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,これ どうなってるんだよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラに 妖狐の衣が…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:14.63,japanese,,0,0,0,,まさか ソラの細胞自体が\N九尾と同調して…。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:44.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,これは…。\Nいったい 何が始まった…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.32,0:10:46.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこにいる人柱力とは違い➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.99,0:10:50.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラの体に\N九尾のチャクラは 膨大すぎた。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:53.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,そこで オレは この10年間…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:57.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,封印術により\N九尾のチャクラをおさえ続けてきた。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:11:01.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,だが… 今 九尾のチャクラを\N解放したことにより➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:06.66,japanese,,0,0,0,,そのバランスは 失われ\Nやがて ソラの体は 乗っ取られる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.66,0:11:11.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,尻尾が９本になったとき\Nソラは 文字どおり 九尾となる。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.13,0:11:14.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,そうなって 初めて\N九尾もどきが本物になるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.97,0:11:16.97,japanese,,0,0,0,,ぐわっ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,テメエ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:32.74,japanese,,0,0,0,,だったら\Nその狐に譲り渡してやるよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:36.31,japanese,,0,0,0,,こんな体!!\Nソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.31,0:11:41.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)そのかわり\Nこんな世界 ぶっ潰してやる！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:48.23,japanese,,0,0,0,,やめろ！ ソラ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.47,0:11:54.47,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)木遁 木錠壁！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:08.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.51,0:12:10.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,サクラちゃん！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:12.98,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:15.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)アスマさん！\Nヤマト隊長！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:19.30,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)先ほどの赤い光は？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:25.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれは… 九尾？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.96,0:12:31.06,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)間違いない… 妖狐の衣だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.06,0:12:35.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,あれは ソラだ。\Nなんですって!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.02,0:12:39.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハッハッハッハッ！ いいぞ ソラ もっとだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:42.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,もっと お前の力を見せてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:49.96,japanese,,0,0,0,,やめろ ソラ！\Nその力 使うんじゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.96,0:12:53.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぅ… うるせえんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.92,japanese,,0,0,0,,影分身の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:06.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,(サクラ)ナルト!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:15.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,遅えぞ シカマル。\N間違いないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:17.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレと赤丸の鼻を なめんなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:22.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラだけじゃねえ\Nアスマ先生とナルトの野郎も一緒だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.25,0:13:25.13,japanese,,0,0,0,,それに もう１人\N里以外のヤツのニオイも…。
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.13,0:13:27.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,敵か？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.95,0:13:30.26,japanese,,0,0,0,,(リー)あれは何でしょう？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.95,0:13:45.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,うがぁ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:47.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,大丈夫 ナルト？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.72,0:14:01.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ…。\N危なかったね。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.04,0:14:04.04,japanese,,0,0,0,,チッ！ だらしねえなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.84,0:14:12.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが相手だ… カズマ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:16.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)この～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.32,0:14:23.32,japanese,,0,0,0,,なぁ ヤマト隊長！\Nオレんときみてえに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.32,0:14:25.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,九尾のチャクラ\Nおさえつけらんねえのかよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.84,0:14:28.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,キミの九尾をおさえられるのは➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,初代様の首飾りが\Nあるからなんだよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:35.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,首飾りを持っていない ソラには\Nムリなんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.99,0:14:40.99,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)ぐぉ～っ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:56.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ！\N(ソラ)そうかよ…\Nそんなに オレがジャマか！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.16,0:14:59.81,japanese,,0,0,0,,いらねえのか！ あっ？\N違う！ ソラ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:03.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレたちは お前に その力を\N使ってほしくねえだけで…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:07.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは… この力とともにある。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:11.09,japanese,,0,0,0,,信用できるのは\Nもう この力だけだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.09,0:15:13.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:16.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)オレを孤独に追いやった\Nお前ら すべてに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.58,0:15:20.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,復讐してやるんだ！ うあぁ～っ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.38,0:15:36.80,japanese,,0,0,0,,ナルト…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:41.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう やなんだよ この力が…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.49,0:15:44.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,人を傷つけるのが…。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.16,0:15:47.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,くぅ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.16,0:15:53.16,japanese,,0,0,0,,あの時…\Nオレは サクラちゃんを傷つけた。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.20,0:16:00.84,japanese,,0,0,0,,((サクラを傷つけたのは…\Nキミだよ ナルト。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:04.83,japanese,,0,0,0,,これからも\Nこの九尾の力に頼れば➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.83,0:16:08.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,自分自身を\N苦しめることになるし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:11.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,(仲間を傷つけてしまう\N力にも なりえる))
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.52,0:16:15.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,だから… だから お前にも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:19.49,japanese,,0,0,0,,その力で\N誰かを傷つけてほしくねえんだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.49,0:16:23.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前に\Nオレの何がわかるってんだよ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.01,0:16:24.41,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレだから わかるんだ!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:31.50,japanese,,0,0,0,,お前に植えつけられた\N九尾の大本は…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.50,0:16:34.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレに封印されてるんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,何を… 言ってる!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.51,0:16:42.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは人柱力だ。
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.18,0:16:45.18,japanese,,0,0,0,,そんな… まさか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.18,0:16:49.85,japanese,,0,0,0,,ソラ。\N来るな！ そんな言葉に➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:54.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは… オレは…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,だまされるか!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.52,0:17:09.12,japanese,,0,0,0,,影真似の術 成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:14.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,シカマル！ チョウジ！\Nいの！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.03,0:17:18.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,クッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:20.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,《アイツら！》
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.02,0:17:23.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,クソッ！ また仲間か！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:25.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,頼むぜ チョウジ！\N(チョウジ)うん！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.51,0:17:28.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,部分倍化の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.51,0:17:30.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,両手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:33.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,うぅ… クソッ！ テメエら！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.36,japanese,,0,0,0,,やった！\Nこれで逃がさねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:49.86,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ソラ)おかしいだろ…\Nお前が九尾を封印してるなら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:53.02,japanese,,0,0,0,,なんで こんなに仲間がいる!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.02,0:17:56.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレは ずっと孤独だった！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.52,0:18:02.71,japanese,,0,0,0,,なのに なんで… なんで お前は！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:07.22,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレだって… 同じだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.22,0:18:10.54,japanese,,0,0,0,,カギの頃は ずっと１人だった。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:14.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,でもな 寂しがってるヒマなんて\Nなかったんだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.52,0:18:19.51,japanese,,0,0,0,,みんなに オレを認めさせてやるって\Nそう思ってたからな。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.51,0:18:23.53,japanese,,0,0,0,,で… やっと出来た仲間が\Nコイツらだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:27.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレには そんな仲間は…。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:31.40,japanese,,0,0,0,,オレが…\Nコイツらが お前の仲間じゃねえか。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:39.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.01,0:18:41.01,japanese,,0,0,0,,いった～。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.03,0:18:45.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,チョウジ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:47.00,japanese,,0,0,0,,いの！\Nわかってる！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.02,0:18:51.72,japanese,,0,0,0,,忍法 心転身の術！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.52,0:18:59.52,japanese,,0,0,0,,やったか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.19,japanese,,0,0,0,,キャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:09.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,どうした いの!?\N(リー)大丈夫ですか!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:14.68,japanese,,0,0,0,,いの！ 心転身は どうした!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:18.67,japanese,,0,0,0,,もう…\Nあの中に人の意識は なかった。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:22.37,japanese,,0,0,0,,(シカマル)なんだって!?\Nチッ！ オレも限界だな。
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.26,0:19:42.58,japanese,,0,0,0,,《しまった！ ３本目までも…》
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:20.60,japanese,,0,0,0,,今回より セットが新装されました。\N司会のヤマトです！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.60,0:21:24.11,japanese,,0,0,0,,ハッキリ言って テコ入れです。\Nアシスタントのサクラで～す！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:27.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)今回は\Nサスケ奪還編からの出題！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.59,0:21:31.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,サスケ君を連れ去るために\N木ノ葉に潜入した４人といえば!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:33.25,japanese,,0,0,0,,音の… あっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.25,0:21:35.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,四人衆！\N(ヤマト)ですが…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:37.94,japanese,,0,0,0,,土遁系の術で チャクラを奪う\N豪腕の…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:40.27,japanese,,0,0,0,,次郎坊！\N(ヤマト)ですが…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:44.59,japanese,,0,0,0,,魔笛で奏でる曲により\N怒鬼３体を操る…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.59,0:21:46.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,多由也。\N(ヤマト)ですが…➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.43,0:21:49.43,japanese,,0,0,0,,６本の腕を持つ 音忍といえば!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.43,0:21:51.95,japanese,,0,0,0,,なぁ コイツと戦ったのって…。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.44,japanese,,0,0,0,,あぁ 確か…。\Nネジですよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:58.28,japanese,,0,0,0,,ていうか アニメーター泣かせの\N手の数だったよな～。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.28,0:22:00.29,japanese,,0,0,0,,(ヤマト)タイムアップ！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:02.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,正解は鬼童丸でした！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.93,0:22:04.93,japanese,,0,0,0,,ちなみに 特技は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.93,0:22:07.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,あやとりだそうです。\N…って 知るか！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.10,0:22:10.10,japanese,,0,0,0,,以上 「あの人は今」でした！\N番組 変わってるし！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.60,0:00:10.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Tsunade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:14.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The defense barrier and\Nthe Reanimation Jutsu have been broken
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and the area around the main gate\Nis returning to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:20.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, the enemy Jutsu that\Nburns down villages in an instant,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:26.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,from Asuma's report, was also stopped\Nbefore it could be executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.33,0:00:28.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.93,0:00:32.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:34.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,that red light...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.83,0:00:35.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:16.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:52.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Despair\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.97,0:02:54.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:58.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:05.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Get angry! Hate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn that anger\Nand hate into power!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Thrash all the people\Nof the Hidden Leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.17,0:03:16.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive them to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.67,0:03:18.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:21.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I...wasn't born to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.77,0:03:23.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,...something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.43,0:03:30.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It is all for the sake of true unification\Nfor the Land of Fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.07,0:03:35.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is\Nnow required, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.30,0:03:38.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck\Nare you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.17,0:03:54.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Asuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:57.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.33,0:03:59.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.43,0:04:04.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:06.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.67,0:04:08.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He used to be a fellow member\Nof the Guardian Shinobi Twelve.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.53,0:04:15.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.87,0:04:17.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck\Ndid you do to Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.03,0:04:20.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,All I did was take your leftovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.77,0:04:29.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...is just like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:30.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.77,0:04:59.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:06.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:11.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this pain...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:14.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:15.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,becoming...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:22.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How...in the world\Ndid you do that to Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.73,0:05:27.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You know more about\Nthe Nine-Tail's attack
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:30.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,on the Hidden Leaf than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.07,0:05:35.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then, the Nine-Tails\Nwas sealed inside a baby...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.30,0:05:37.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,at the cost of\Nthe Fourth Hokage's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:42.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hidden Leaf\Nobtained the Nine-Tails
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.97,0:05:45.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and we couldn't afford to miss\Nthat opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.60,0:05:49.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Nine-Tails\Nwent on its rampage,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:51.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,we obtained the scattered Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:57.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We cultivated it and then implanted it\Nin Sora five years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:59.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:00.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is your...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.27,0:06:06.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Hidden Leaf had obtained\Na significant power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.10,0:06:11.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We also wanted to obtain such a power\Nin order to protect the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.70,0:06:13.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.63,0:06:21.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew...\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:26.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.47,0:06:32.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.27,0:06:42.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that was...\Nthat was Sora's voice...crying out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:47.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...why wasn't I able\Nto pick up on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.37,0:06:51.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And here I was the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.27,0:06:54.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,who could understand\Nhis pain and his cries...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.97,0:07:00.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same\Nback then, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.43,0:07:05.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes around Sora...\Nwatching him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.00,0:07:09.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Those cold and repulsive eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,As if they were saying,\N"Get out of here."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.67,0:07:21.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew...they were the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.63,0:07:27.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as those eyes\Nwatching {\i1}me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:34.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.07,0:07:46.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes of the adults looking at me,\Nas if wanting to stab me to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:50.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's those same eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that matter now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.73,0:07:56.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:01.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes that only saw us\Nas monsters. Isolated us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:03.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And on top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:06.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,you try to use us\Nat your own convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.67,0:08:14.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the time with Gaara...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.33,0:08:20.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you adults even attempt\Nto think about how we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:25.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, Sora... Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.90,0:08:28.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why was it necessary to put\Nthis monster inside him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.27,0:08:45.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why do this to Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:47.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:55.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.27,0:09:07.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.63,0:09:12.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You all stay away from me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.27,0:09:20.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I won't be tricked any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:22.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.93,0:09:25.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,and then try to befriend me\Nlike nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:31.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Special power, my foot!\NYou tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:32.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:34.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And when all is said and done,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.13,0:09:40.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,you're also just one\Nof the Hidden Leaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.13,0:09:41.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.30,0:09:51.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.47,0:10:09.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on...?\NNine-Tail's Cloak...on Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:14.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me Sora's cells\Nare merging with the Nine-Tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world has begun here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the Jinchuriki there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.43,0:10:50.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the Nine-Tails Chakra is too massive\Nfor Sora's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.37,0:10:54.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I continued to suppress\Nthe Nine-Tails Chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:57.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,with a Sealing Jutsu for\Nthese past ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:02.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,However...with the Nine-Tails Chakra\Nnow having been released,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.30,0:11:06.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,the balance has been lost and\NSora's body is being taken over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the Nine-Tails has\Nformed all nine tails,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:11.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora will literally turn into\Nthe Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.63,0:11:15.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then will the imitation\NNine-Tails become the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.53,0:11:21.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.43,0:11:34.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...\NI'll turn over this body to that fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.47,0:11:35.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:42.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash...this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.33,0:11:47.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:53.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Wood Style!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Domed Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:06.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.93,0:12:10.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:12.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:13.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.37,0:12:15.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.90,0:12:18.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What was the red light\Nfrom before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.57,0:12:24.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:27.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Nine-Tail's Cloak.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.63,0:12:33.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.97,0:12:34.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.90,0:12:37.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:39.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,More.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Revel more of your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.90,0:12:49.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Sora!\NDon't use that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.87,0:12:53.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.50,0:12:56.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.33,0:13:05.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.37,0:13:13.63,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Shikamaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.07,0:13:15.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.63,0:13:17.80,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate\Nmy and Akamaru's noses!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:19.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Asuma Sensei and Naruto\Nare also with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's the scent of\None other person not from the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,An enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:29.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.10,0:13:46.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:57.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You okay, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.23,0:13:58.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.47,0:14:00.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a close one, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,How sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.13,0:14:10.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm your opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.43,0:14:12.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Kazuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.77,0:14:23.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato! Can't you control\Nthe Nine-Tails Chakra like you did
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.77,0:14:25.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,when that happened to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:28.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I can control your Nine-Tails Chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.60,0:14:31.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,because you have\Nthe First Hokage's necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It won't work on Sora,\Nhe doesn't have a necklace.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.13,0:14:52.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:54.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I that much of a hindrance?!\NYou don't need me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.57,0:14:58.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.40,0:14:59.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.10,0:15:03.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,We just don't want you\Nto use that power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...one with this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.53,0:15:11.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,This power is the only thing\NI can trust now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.30,0:15:12.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:18.47,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have revenge on all of you guys\Nwho drove me to loneliness!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:36.07,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.23,0:15:43.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sick of people getting hurt...\Nwith this power...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.57,0:15:51.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then...I hurt Sakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:16:00.57,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the one\N{\i1}who hurt Sakura, Naruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.77,0:16:04.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You'll end up tormenting yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:07.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}if you rely on\N{\i1}the power of the Nine-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.37,0:16:11.17,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it could turn into a power\N{\i1}that hurts your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:12.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.80,0:16:18.30,english,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I don't want you hurting\Nanyone with that power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:22.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't know\Nanything about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:31.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The origin of the Nine-Tails\Nyou've been implanted with...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.93,0:16:33.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,is sealed inside me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.93,0:16:37.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you...talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.80,0:16:45.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you...saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:46.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.97,0:16:49.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.37,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.30,0:16:55.90,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be tricked by those words!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.30,0:17:08.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,The Shadow Possession Jutsu\Nis a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.70,0:17:13.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikamaru, Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.33,0:17:13.77,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:19.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They've come...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.83,0:17:22.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! More friends, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:24.70,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Choji!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.90,0:17:25.53,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.43,0:17:28.10,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Partial Expansion Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.10,0:17:30.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:32.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:34.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.93,0:17:36.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Now he won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.53,0:17:45.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:49.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got the Nine-Tails\Nsealed inside you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.13,0:17:52.73,english,,0000,0000,0000,,why do you have so many friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:56.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all alone the whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.83,0:18:01.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, why...why do you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:05.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same with me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.83,0:18:10.40,english,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little,\NI was always by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:14.33,english,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't have\Nthe time to be lonesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.17,0:18:18.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to get everyone\Nto acknowledge me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.80,0:18:22.83,english,,0000,0000,0000,,And these are the friends I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:27.03,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no friends like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.07,0:18:31.23,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...these guys are all your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:40.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:43.93,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Choji...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:45.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.17,0:18:46.87,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.03,0:18:51.50,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja Art:\NMind Transfer Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:58.97,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:07.20,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Ino?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:08.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:12.43,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Ino! What happened with\Nthe Mind Transfer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:18.67,english,,0000,0000,0000,,There was no...\Nhuman consciousness inside him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.00,english,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.53,0:19:23.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,I've reached my limit, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.90,0:19:42.13,english,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh no! It's his third tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.33,0:21:39.60,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Yamato!\NSomething's wrong with Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.00,0:21:44.27,english,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the Nine-Tails Chakra\Nhas leaked out...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60